Name: Location Code
Description: Unique identifier assigned to the location.  (Currently used as a key when exchanging information with McKesson PACS via the PACS Integration module.)

Name: Default Label Printer
Description: The default label printer for this location

Name: Default ID card Printer
Description: The default id card printer for this location

Name: Default Wristband Printer
Description: The default wristband printer for this location

Name: Name to print on ID card
Description: The name to use when printing a location on an id card
